<MainLayout>
    <h1>POST - Digital Folder Link</h1>
    
    ## Endpoint
    **URL**: `https://app.firmeasy.legal/api/v1/digital/carpeta/enlace`  
    **Description**: This endpoint allows the user to add a digital link to a specific folder.

    ## Request Body
    - `carpeta_id` (string, required): The ID of the folder to which the digital link will be added.
    - `tiempo` (integer): The time duration for the digital link in hours.

    ### Example Request Body
    <pre class="astro-code bg-slate-800 text-white">
    {"{"}
        "carpeta_id": "3b9266a1-2f13-4980-85d9-14edaa84a4d6",
        "tiempo": 5
    {"}"}
    </pre>

    ## Example Request (cURL)
    <pre class="astro-code bg-slate-800 text-white">
    curl --location 'https://app.firmeasy.legal/api/v1/digital/carpeta/enlace' \\
    --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\
    --data '{"{"}
        "carpeta_id": "3b9266a1-2f13-4980-85d9-14edaa84a4d6",
        "tiempo": 5
    {"}"}'
    </pre>

    ## Response
    Upon successful execution, the response will have a status code of 200 and a JSON body with the following fields.

    ### Example Response
    <pre class="astro-code bg-slate-800 text-white">
    {"{"}
        "success": true,
        "enlace": "https://app.firmeasy.legal/link/3b9266a1-2f13-4980-85d9-14edaa84a4d6",
        "message": "Link created successfully"
    {"}"}
    </pre>

    ### JSON Schema
    <pre class="astro-code bg-slate-800 text-white">
    {"{"}
        "success": "boolean",
        "enlace": "string",
        "message": "string"
    {"}"}
    </pre>

    ## Authorization
    **Bearer Token**: This request uses a Bearer Token from the Firmeasy API Production collection.

    ## Headers
    - `Content-Type`: `application/json`

</MainLayout>
